  image: {fileID: 10905, guid: 0000000000000000f000000000000000, type: 0}
  description: "The Myling is a spirit of a child murdered by its mother, often returning
    to haunt her as a punishment. \nThe Myling lingers near the place, where the
    body was hidden - screaming and sobbing in the darkness. \nIt can take physical
    form in the shape of a giant black bird with a human head. "
